claim.claim-text:
The method according to claim 1 or 2, wherein the reference value set is configured by the network device;
the reference value set is predefined; or
the reference value set is determined by a higher layer of the first terminal device.

The method according to any one of claims 1 to 3, wherein the first value is used to indicate a transmit power on a first orthogonal frequency division multiplexing OFDM symbol on which the first signal is located;
the first value is used to indicate a transmit power on a first resource element RE of a first OFDM symbol on which the first signal is located; or
the first value is used to indicate a transmit power on a first resource block RB of a first OFDM symbol on which the first signal is located.

The method according to any one of claims 1 to 6, wherein the first signal comprises a physical sidelink shared channel PSSCH, and the indication information is carried in the PSSCH;
the first signal comprises a physical sidelink control channel PSCCH, and the indication information is carried in the PSCCH; or
the first signal comprises a physical sidelink feedback channel PSFCH, and the indication information is carried in the PSFCH.

The communications apparatus according to claim 25 or 26, wherein the reference value set is configured by the network device;
the reference value set is predefined; or
the reference value set is determined by a higher layer of the communications apparatus.

The communications apparatus according to any one of claims 25 to 27, wherein the first value is used to indicate a transmit power on a first orthogonal frequency division multiplexing OFDM symbol on which the first signal is located;
the first value is used to indicate a transmit power on a first resource element RE of a first OFDM symbol on which the first signal is located; or
the first value is used to indicate a transmit power on a first resource block RB of a first OFDM symbol on which the first signal is located.

The communications apparatus according to any one of claims 25 to 30, wherein the first signal comprises a physical sidelink shared channel PSSCH, and the indication information is carried in the PSSCH;
the first signal comprises a physical sidelink control channel PSCCH, and the indication information is carried in the PSCCH; or
the first signal comprises a physical sidelink feedback channel PSFCH, and the indication information is carried in the PSFCH.
